The paper proposes an algorithm based on deep learning for inventory optimization, which falls under the category of machine learning and optimization. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also deals with optimization problems, which suggests that it could belong to cs.OR (Operations Research) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Finally, the paper uses real-world data, which could suggest that it belongs to cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
